OL,6,FNorth West politicians from across the
OL,7,Fpolitical divide have united in their
OL,8,Fbacking of of those wrongfully
OL,9,Fimplicated in the Post Office Scandal.
OL,11,FSpeaking on March's , Andy Carter,
OL,12,FWarrington South's Conservative MP
OL,13,Fsaid: "Usually there are very
OL,14,Fseparated powers between parliament
OL,15,Fand the judiciary - You don't want the
OL,16,Fpeople that are making the laws to
OL,17,Falso enforce them as you have to have
OL,18,Fseparation of powers.
