OL,6,F"In this instance the time that it
OL,7,Fwould have taken to have each
OL,8,Findividual case assessed by the courts
OL,9,Fwould have taken such a long time that
OL,10,FI think the Justice secretary Alex
OL,11,FChalk has done the right thing."
OL,13,F"I do though think there are some
OL,14,Fareas we still need to deal with,
OL,15,Fparticularly employees of the Post
OL,16,FOffice who may not have been
OL,17,Fprosecuted but may well have been
OL,18,Fdisciplined or dismissed from their
OL,19,Femployment and have their reputation
OL,20,Fimpacted.
