OL,6,FMr Smith said: "I think the government
OL,7,Fare doing the right thing. It is very
OL,8,Funusual but I think because of the
OL,9,Fcircumstances and this terrible
OL,10,Fmiscarriage - one of the worst - in
OL,11,FBritish history, I think it's it's the
OL,12,Fright thing to do."
OL,14,FCllr Smart Said: "It's four years
OL,15,Fsince the High Court ruled on these
OL,16,Fwrongful convictions and I think it's
OL,17,Fright that this legislation is coming
OL,18,Fforward.
